@startuml Add to cart state machine
[*] --> Idle

Idle: cartStatus: 'idle'
Idle: cartItems: [] | [...cartItems]
Idle: error: undefined

Idle -down-> Pending : addToCart
Pending: cartItems: [...cartItems, optimistically added cart item]
Pending: cartStatus: 'pending'
Pending: error: undefined

state condition1 <<choice>>

Pending -down--> condition1 : updateCartItems
condition1 --> Success : success
condition1 --> Error : random failure

Success: cartItems: [...cartItems, newItem]
Success: cartStatus: 'success'
Success: error: undefined

Error: cartItems: [...prevCartItems]
Error: cartStatus: 'error'
Error: error: Error

Success --> Idle : message success
Error --> Idle : rollback to previous items \nmessage error

Idle -right--> [*]
@enduml